{"tid":977154,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂:重芝士蛋糕條-復活疑似雪壞了的cream cheese","createTime":"2019-01-11T03:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T13:12:06.000Z","uid":30742,"like":46,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b36ece52d8648d210a7bf598ba9afd54c00af852","tid":977154,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pPmA975.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpPmA975.jpg&h=04fbc2d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y6Ht_Qha1CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY6Ht_Qha1CA&d=VeVOV7LkbUF9DlidzKtQe%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=eedf4bb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y6Ht_Qha1CA</a><br />\n我每次行開烘焙鋪，都會忍唔住買一大舊cream cheese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時總會諗到千百樣方法整左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到去分完裝就無左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但分裝後放下格好易會發霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放上格佢又變豆腐渣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但咁樣絕對唔係變壞！只係texture有d唔同左！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要加多少少步驟！做芝士蛋糕絕對無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要好好味！出面三四十蚊件，自己做三四十蚊個！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/01/cream-cheese-easy-baked-cheese-cake.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F01%2Fcream-cheese-easy-baked-cheese-cake.html&d=VeVOV7LkbUF9DlidzKtQe%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3f3fbc93\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/01/cream-cheese-easy-baked-cheese-cake.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=VeVOV7LkbUF9DlidzKtQe%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f74904a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=VeVOV7LkbUF9DlidzKtQe%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=748efed5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=VeVOV7LkbUF9DlidzKtQe%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=82314be3\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"87757072480fedb668c311d15e3383bab7343a70","tid":977154,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sco